NOTICE -- exynos990-KernelSU-Next-SuSFS

This repository is a derivative of the Linux kernel and Samsung's open-source
kernel release for the Galaxy S20 series (Exynos 990 / universal9830), with
KernelSU-Next and SuSFS integrated. It is distributed under GPL-2.0 (see COPYING).

