----------------------------

* Linux kernel -- GPL-2.0. Copyright the Linux kernel contributors.

* Samsung Galaxy S20 (Exynos 990 / universal9830) kernel source -- GPL-2.0,
  Samsung Open Source Release Center (https://opensource.samsung.com):
    - SM-G985F_SWA_13_Opensource  (y2s, trunk: shared kernel source + drivers)
    - SM-G980F_13_Opensource      (x1s, device tree + defconfig)
    - SM-G988B_13_Opensource      (z3s, device tree + defconfig)

* KernelSU-Next -- GPL-2.0. https://github.com/KernelSU-Next/KernelSU-Next
